characteristic.__text: Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelords Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible enemy unit within 12" of them to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
For the rest of the turn, subtract 1 from the Damage characteristic of the target’s melee weapons.
Your Hero Phase

Pick a friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelord Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible enemy unit within 18" of them that has not been picked to be the target of this ability this turn to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
Roll a number of dice equal to the number of models in the target unit. For each 6, inflict 1 mortal damage on that unit. If any enemy models were slain by this spell, **Heal(D3)** the caster.
**^^Spell^^**, **^^Unlimited^^**
Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelords Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible enemy unit within 12" of them to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
The target has **^^Strike-last^^** until the start of your next turn
Once Per Battle, Any Combat Phase
Pick an enemy **^^Hero^^** in combat with this unit to be the target.
The target has **^^Strike-last^^** for the rest of the turn.
Reaction: Opponent declared a **^^Spell^^** ability for a **^^Wizard^^** within 18" of this unit
Roll a D3. On a 2+, inflict an amount of mortal damage on the caster equal to the roll. If the target is destroyed by this ability, do not resolve the effect of that **^^Spell^^** ability.
Ignore modifiers to save rolls for shooting attacks that target this unit (positive and negative).
Once Per Turn (Army), End of Any Turn
Pick up to 3 friendly **^^Deadwalkers^^** units in combat to be the targets.

For each target:
• Make a pile-in move.
• Then, pick an enemy unit in combat with the target and roll a D3. On a 2+, inflict an amount of mortal damage on that enemy unit equal to the roll.
Add 1 to casting rolls for friendly **^^Vampire^^** units that are not in combat and add 1 to wound rolls for combat attacks made by friendly VAMPIRE units that charged in the same turn.

Add 1 to the Rend characteristic of melee weapons used by friendly **^^Deathrattle^^** units that charged in the same turn for attacks that target a unit that has fewer models than the attacking unit.
You can pick 1 additional target when using the ‘Deathly Invocation’ ability.
Once Per Turn, Your Hero Phase
Pick another friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelords^^** unit within this unit’s combat range to be the target.
Roll a dice. On a 2+, if the target is not in combat, it can move D6". If the target is in combat, it can make a pile-in move.
Pick a friendly **^^Deathrattle^^** or **^^Deadwalkers^^** unit that has 2 or more models and is wholly within 12" of this unit to be the target.
Add D6 to the target’s control score for the rest of the turn.
You can re-roll charge rolls for this unit in your charge phase.
Once Per Turn (Army), End of Any Turn
Pick each friendly **^^Vampire^^** unit that used a **^^Fight^^** ability this turn to be the targets.
**Heal (D3)** each target. **Heal (2D3)** the target instead if it destroyed an enemy unit this turn using a **^^Fight^^** ability
Deployment Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Deathrattle^^** or **^^Deadwalkers^^** unit that has not been deployed.
Set up that unit in reserve **in the grave**. It has now been deployed. You cannot set up more friendly units **in the grave** than there are on the battlefield.
**^^Deploy^^**
Once Per Turn (Army), Any Movement Phase
Pick a friendly non-**^^Unique Deathrattle^^** or **^^Deadwalkers^^** unit that started the battle with 2 or more models and that has been destroyed to be the target.

Set up a replacement unit with half the number of models from the target unit (rounding up) wholly within 12" of a friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelords Hero^^**  or wholly within 6" of a terrain feature. It must be set up more than 9" from all enemy units.


If it is your movement phase, you can set up the replacement unit more than3" from all enemy units instead of more than 9", but if you set it up within 9" of any enemy units, it cannot use **^^Charge^^** abilities this turn.
Once Per Turn (Army), Any Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Soulblight Gravelords Hero^^** to use this ability, then pick up to 3 friendly **^^Deathrattle^^** or **^^Deadwalkers^^** units wholly within 12" of that Hero to be the targets.

For each target:
• If the target is damaged, **Heal (3)** the target.
• If the target is not damaged, return a number of slain models to it with a combined Health characteristic of up to 3.
Your Movement Phase
Pick a friendly unit that is **in the grave**.
Set up that unit wholly within 6" of a terrain feature and more than 9" from all enemy units
